获取链信息
curl -X GET "http://127.0.0.1:5000/chain"

新增一条记录
curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:5000/record/new" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d'
{
  "name": "张三",
  "type": "远程支持",
  "scope": "数据库",
  "detail": "解决数据库启动异常问题",
  "region": "杭州",
  "tag": "MySQL",
  "time": "2019-12-22",
  "duration": "1H",
  "product": "测试项目",
  "department": "软件研发中心-研发一部",
  "contact": "李四"
}
'

注册一个新的节点
curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:5000/nodes/register" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d'
{
  "nodes": ["http://192.168.0.1:5000"]
}
'

对该节点的权威性进行校验
curl -X GET "http://127.0.0.1:5000/nodes/resolve"
